### Order API - HTTP Requests

# Configuração de ambientes
@Order.Api_Local = http://localhost:5160
@Order.Api_Docker = http://localhost:8080

### Criar Order - Local
POST {{Order.Api_Local}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clienteId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "valorTotal": 150.50,
  "status": "CRIANDO",
  "dataCriacao": "2024-01-15T10:30:00"
}

###

